headline: How Recent Engine Replacement News Impacts Airbus Stock’s 2025 Value Potential
summary: Thinking about whether you should hold, buy, or sell Airbus stock? You are not alone. With the share price recently closing at 195.72 and up 1.0% in the past week, Airbus continues to catch the eye of anyone interested in the aviation industry. Over the last month, the stock has soared by 9.8%, and it has delivered an impressive 22.2% return so far this year.
